<author>bhjt ʿdly, bhjt ʿdly</author>
<title>ymkn ạ̉kwn</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ymkn ạ̉kwn gẖlṭt ạ̹mbạrḥ wbqt kl ḥyạty ḍyạʿ
 lkn tẖqty ạ̹n ạ̹nt tsạmḥ wtṣḥḥ fy ạlạ̉wḍạʿ
 ạlqrạr - yạrby ạkẖtbrny wạksẖf ly ʿ ạlly fy qlby
 ạrjʿ lk wtṭmny bwqwfk dạymạaⁿ jnby
 2- ymkn ạ̉kwn ḍʿyf jwạyạ wʿywby̱ tạʿbạny̱ ktyr
 wlạ ynfʿny̱ ạ̉lạqy lhạ nhạyẗ gẖyr ạ̹ny̱ ạljạ̉ lk yạ qdyr
 3- ymkn ạ̉kwn msẖ qạdr ạ̉nsy̱ gẖlṭạty wgẖlṭạt ạlgẖyr
 ʿạyz ạ̉tʿlm ạ̹zạy ạ̉nsy̱ sẖr ạ̹kẖwạty wạ̉qạblh bkẖyr
 4- ymkn ạ̉kwn mḥtạj lạ̉mạn nfsy ạ̉ḥsh wlw lḥẓạt
 wạ̉nsy̱ mkẖạwfy wḥzn zmạn wkạ̉nh rạḥ ʿny wmạt</lyrics>
</song>